{"id":703,"date":"2024-08-27T14:53:00","date_gmt":"2024-08-27T19:53:00","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/endhazing.sl.ua.edu\/?p=703"},"modified":"2025-12-09T14:55:17","modified_gmt":"2025-12-09T20:55:17","slug":"kappa-sigma","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/endhazing.sl.ua.edu\/posts\/2024\/2024\/kappa-sigma\/","title":{"rendered":"Kappa Sigma"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>This is part of the <a href=\"https:\/\/endhazing.sl.ua.edu\/hazing-transparency-report\/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"918\">Hazing Transparency Report<\/a>, which contains <a href=\"https:\/\/endhazing.sl.ua.edu\/hazing-transparency-report\/#terminology\">terminology definitions<\/a> and <a href=\"https:\/\/endhazing.sl.ua.edu\/hazing-transparency-report\/#rules\">rules defined<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull is-style-elevated is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignwide is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading alignwide\">Fall 2024<\/h2>\n\n\n<div class=\"ua_component_wrapper  \"><div class=\"ua_layout--grid\" >\n<div  >\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-left\">Incident: 8\/23\/2024<br>Location: On Campus<\/p>\n\n<\/div>\n\n<div  >\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-left\">Reported: 8\/27\/2024<br>Reported by: Hotline Report<\/p>\n\n<\/div>\n\n<div  >\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-left\">Investigation: Joint, initially GSU-led<\/p>\n\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Description<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Kappa Sigma new members were ordered to consume food items and concoctions in excess causing some new member(s) to vomit and forced, coerced or intimidated ingestion of concoctions.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"ua_component_wrapper  \"><div class=\"ua_layout--grid\" >\n<div  >\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Rules Violations<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Article III.B.(2)a. &#8211; Hazing<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Article III.B.(2)b. &#8211; Hazing Policy<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Findings<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Hazing: Forced, coerced or intimidated consumption of food items and concoctions in excess.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Individuals Responsible: 5<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Arrests<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>None<\/p>\n\n<\/div>\n\n<div  >\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Sanctions<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Disciplinary Probation from 10\/30\/2024 until 12\/31\/2025<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Interim Measures \u2013 Issued 9\/24\/2024<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Loss of all Social Privileges through 12\/31\/2024<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Decreased Social Privileges- Spring 2025 (6 events)<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Required co-host for hazing prevention speaker for IFC community &#8211; Fall 2025<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Education Assessment Fee<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Executive Officer Training<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Establishment of Harm and Risk Reduction Committee<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Establishment of Alumni Advisory Board<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Facility Updates \u2013 Enhanced Safety and Security Measures<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>National Headquarters sanctions<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div>\n<\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Fall 2024 Description Kappa Sigma new members were ordered to consume food items and concoctions in excess causing some new member(s) to vomit and forced, coerced or intimidated ingestion of concoctions.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[9],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-703","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","hentry","category-9"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/endhazing.sl.ua.edu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/703","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/endhazing.sl.ua.edu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/endhazing.sl.ua.edu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"au